{
  "stem": "9665.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The Eislands, I still don't know, Harry and Lola Eisland, where they stayed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But for us, they were very, very old people, because he was already 29, and I was 21.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So looking at him and her, and she were 30, that they were already with one foot in their grave.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, that everything is relative.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We stayed with Joseph for two nights.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, we slept on one bed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And whenever I go to Antwerp, he mentioned that, you know, that we had an affair, that two couples.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We couldn't think of anything else.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We stayed two nights.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And from there we went to Brussels by train.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we stayed in a brothel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you know why a brothel?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because there's no check up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So when we went to that brothel, we had the address in Antwerp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The mirrors were on the ceiling and on the wall.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And full of Germans in the other rooms.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You don't have to write down your name.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The woman in charge knew that we were Jews, but that address was given to us in Antwerp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was-- we were told that it is safe.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She told us, if something happens, because sometimes they're checking up the German soldiers in that brothel, you know?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then she will take us-- there were three houses next to each other.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the place is-- the, the square, I remember, is called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Three houses next to each other.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How I remember that?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't think about it this morning, but it comes to me now.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we actually had a reasonably good time there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Joseph and Rosie came to visit us, stayed with us three days.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We stayed there four days.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then-- I forgot to tell you something.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
